# Reconverse — no client-side env vars are needed.
#
# MC transport is configured server-side on Vercel:
#   MC_API_INTERNAL  (Production)  ->  public URL of Motorverse Mission Control
#
# Frontend hits same-origin /api/v1/* and the Vercel function api/proxy.ts
# forwards to MC. If MC_API_INTERNAL is unset, /api/v1/* returns
# 503 { ok: false, error: 'mc_unreachable' }.
